    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If a conceal is set by a plugin, to my knowledge, there is no way to disable it when conceal is enabled. Yes, all conceal can be disabled, but if I only want particular conceals, there is no way to override some of the conceal highlights to disable them. My thought is to do something similar to `nospell` where `nospell` is higher priority than `spell` and will always override it.\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-25T15:42:45Z",
