            "body": "yes to both, I should have been more specific. Semi-looking into this and it feels like I should add some extra state [here](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/fb0dc825e9bbb9bed0d98b8c7f6ac1d117408c90/src/nvim/decoration.h#L96) similar to how spell works to turn off conceal at particular rows/columns.",
